parameters:
"This is the orphanage where Rise was. At first glance, it
looks like a peaceful and nice place, doesn't it?"

"Yes, I too thought it was a good place until not so long
ago."

"They were supposed to have moved to a better facility built
by the country."
"But in reality, they had all already been sold off."

"This orphanage, along with others managed by Nolz and his
group, was gathering and raising children to be sold off to
nobles and those involved in shady dealings."

"Thinking that my remittances were also used for such things
makes me feel so helpless."

"But that's exactly why we're going to catch him today and
put an end to this."

"Beyond here is the underground sewer. But actually, even
further down is where Nolz's human trafficking facility is
located."
A notice is posted on the door.

Due to the aging of the building, we have relocated to the
newly established orphanage.
